{"tid":1284327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎防中共推假民主 扮退讓","createTime":"2019-07-04T06:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T09:18:31.000Z","uid":34047,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47913a7d6f502373124bc7d8a67b6058fc64c449","tid":1284327,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/697033560746082/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347501365699305%2Fposts%2F697033560746082%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=fd4c61ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/697033560746082/</a><br />\n<br />\n美中攻防戰&mdash;&mdash;香港國會普選<br />\n<br />\n中共不是省油的燈，二十多年來中共一直不容許香港普選國會，現在兩日間突然透過不同人士發言談及政改普選。這個可能是以退為進的策略。<br />\n<br />\n因為美國的《香港人權與民主保證法案》將要通過，並且可能限定香港要於 2020 年進行國會普選。若等到該法案通過後，香港才重啓政改，這就必須乎合美國規定，中共沒有走動空間。而且，這就是香港遵從了美國的法案，便間接承認了美國擁有香港的管治權。<br />\n<br />\n因此，中共現在打算先行推動政改，製造一個類似普選的假東西，然後會有議員代表香港人接受。那麼就搶先在美國的法案通過前，使香港有「民主」，減低了美國的影響，也削弱了該法案的力量。同時，香港就會出現一群主張「袋住先」的人，大量輿論會導向接受中共的方案。之後，國會普選就沒有了，一切返回原狀，先烈的血白流，義士枉然被控⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n這次，是中共以退為進，香港人現在有兩個選擇。一、有法治守信用的美國法案；二、沒法律亂撒謊的中共引誘。而今次，是香港向美國求援的，道義上就該接受美國出手。若香港選錯了就萬劫不復。<br />\n<br />\n現在是中共疲弱之時，牠退讓一步，香港就要向前推進十步。這機會，是用血換來的，不容任何政棍代表香港放棄！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157231814597225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157231814597225%3Fs%3D600287265%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=d687d7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157231814597225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157230744967225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157230744967225%3Fs%3D600287265%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=65193338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157230744967225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ef9acf28980759d7812b3574e96c7c8d5798ecb2","tid":1284327,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"作者/來源: 敗傲籮即高 嘥仁時 （Bio Sciences）"},{"pid":"dd16b71b9a5fca33bb1a9cf6ee9d1f71d1d30d0b","tid":1284327,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"根本就玩緊 轉移視線 <br />\n咪中計 一單還一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7c284da98db52399808be01b101ec6352f0072","tid":1284327,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd16b71b9a5fca33bb1a9cf6ee9d1f71d1d30d0b","tid":1284327,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"根本就玩緊 轉移視線 <br />\n咪中計 一單還一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"冇錯 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"de3863072c13416f6d262222008610f10f332687","tid":1284327,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"512071de72bdd06f6785c47e925f2cd6bf90b19a","tid":1284327,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"share去fb"},{"pid":"7df7a8c7de94a4dcb90e13bcc584d4bda539dbd2","tid":1284327,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"講得岩<br />\n但中共有冇勇氣推假普選"},{"pid":"5e32fb00d97c2991aa16cd4f37fac7b0387c949d","tid":1284327,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df7a8c7de94a4dcb90e13bcc584d4bda539dbd2","tid":1284327,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"講得岩<br />\n但中共有冇勇氣推假普選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"或者其中一著係整個假既普選<b